   Kotthoff, Ulrich, Univ Hamburg, Hamburg, Germany.
   de Beaulieu, Jacques-Louis, Univ Paul Cezanne Europole Arbois, Puyricard, France.
   Drescher-Schneider, Ruth, Kainbach Bei Graz, Graz, Austria.},
DOI = {10.1177/0959683610384162},
Keywords = {climate changes; Holocene; Mediterranean; pollen; seasonality},
Keywords-Plus = {LAGO-DELLACCESA TUSCANY; SEA-SURFACE TEMPERATURE; VEGETATION HISTORY;
