   Sun, Jian; Ma, Baibing, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Geog Sci \& Nat Resources Res, Key Lab Ecosyst Network Observat \& Modelling, Synth Res Ctr Chinese Ecosyst Res Network, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.
   Ma, Baibing, Changan Univ, Sch Earth Sci \& Resource, Xian 710000, Shaanxi, Peoples R China.
   Lu, Xuyang, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Mt Hazards \& Environm, Key Lab Mt Surface Proc \& Ecol Regulat, Chengdu 610041, Sichuan, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1002/ldr.2822},
Keywords = {biomass allocation; climate elements; grassland practice; soil nutrient;
   vegetation dynamic},
Keywords-Plus = {FINE-ROOT DYNAMICS; PLANT BIOMASS; RANGELAND DEGRADATION; CARBON
