   Marino, Maria Adele, Univ Messina, Dept Biomed Sci \& Morphol \& Funct Imaging, Policlin Univ G Martino, Messina, Italy.
   Clauser, Paola, Univ Udine, Dept Med \& Biol Sci, Inst Diagnost Radiol, Azienda Osped Univ,S Maria Misericordia, Udine, Italy.
   Preidler, Klaus, Diagnosezentrum Meidling, Vienna, Austria.},
DOI = {10.1007/s00330-015-4075-7},
Keywords = {Breast cancer; MRI; Scoring system; Reader experience; Sensitivity and
