   Kirst, Matias; Resende, Marcio F. R., Jr., Univ Florida, Sch Forest Resources \& Conservat, Gainesville, FL 32611 USA.
   Kirst, Matias; Resende, Marcio F. R., Jr., Univ Florida, Genet Inst, Gainesville, FL 32611 USA.
   de los Campos, Gustavo, Michigan State Univ, Dept Stat, E Lansing, MI 48824 USA.},
