   Broussais, Florence; Sesques, Pierre, Hop Lyon Sud, Serv Hematol, Hosp Civils Lyon, Pierre Benite, France.
   Sesques, Pierre; Traverse-Glehen, Alexandra, Univ Claude Bernard Lyon 1, Ctr Rech Cancerol Lyon, Lyon, France.
   Sesques, Pierre; Traverse-Glehen, Alexandra, Univ Claude Bernard Lyon 1, INSERM, UMR S1052, Lyon, France.
   Sesques, Pierre; Traverse-Glehen, Alexandra, Univ Claude Bernard Lyon 1, CNRS, UMR 5286, Lyon, France.
