   Postma, Merel; Dewulf, Jeroen, Univ Ghent, Fac Vet Med, Vet Epidemiol Unit, Dept Reprod Obstet \& Herd Hlth, Salisburylaan 133, B-9820 Merelbeke, Belgium.
   McCutcheon, Gerard, Pig Dev Dept, Teagasc Oak Pk, Carlow, Ireland.
   Manzanilla, Edgar Garcia, Univ Coll Dublin, Sch Vet Med, Dublin 4, Ireland.},
