   Antoniadis, Anestis, Univ Cape Town, Dept Stat Sci, PD Hahn Bldg, Cape Town, South Africa.
   De Feis, Italia, Italian Natl Res Council, Inst Applicat Comp M Picone, Naples, Italy.
   Goude, Yannig; Lagache, Audrey, EDF, OSIRIS Dept, 7 Bd Gaspard Monge, F-91120 Palaiseau, France.
   Goude, Yannig, Univ Paris Sud, F-91405 Orsay, France.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ijforecast.2020.04.001},
Keywords = {Short-term load forecasting; Semi-parametric additive model; Random
   forest; Wavelets; Penalised least-squares},
