   Zhou, Xiao-Nong, MOH, Key Lab Parasite \& Vector Biol, Shanghai 200025, Peoples R China.
   Zhou, Xiao-Nong, WHO Collaborating Ctr Trop Dis, Shanghai 200025, Peoples R China.},
