   Saathoff, C., Univ Koblenz Landau, WeST Inst Web Sci \& Technol, D-56070 Koblenz, Germany.
   Escalante, H. J., Univ Autonoma Nuevo Leon, Grad Program Syst Engn, San Nicolas De Los Garza 66450, NL, Mexico.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.cviu.2011.05.005},
