   Wanyan, Tingyi, Indiana Univ, Sch Informat Comp \& Engn, Bloomington, IN USA.
   Nadkarni, Girish N., Icahn Sch Med Mt Sinai, Div Nephrol, Dept Med, New York, NY USA.
   Nadkarni, Girish N., Icahn Sch Med Mt Sinai, Charles Bronfman Inst Personalized Med, New York, NY USA.
   Wang, Fei, Weill Cornell Med, Dept Populat Hlth Sci, New York, NY USA.
   Glicksberg, Benjamin S., Icahn Sch Med Mt Sinai, Dept Genet \& Genom Sci, New York, NY USA.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.cvdhj.2022.07.074},
