   McQueen, Peter; Gates, Lucy; Bowen, Catherine, Univ Southampton, Arthrit Res UK Ctr Sport Exercise \& Osteoarthrit, Southampton, Hants, England.
   Gates, Lucy; Arden, Nigel, Univ Oxford, Arthrit Res UK Ctr Sport Exercise \& Osteoarthriti, Oxford, England.
