   Martin, Oscar, Univ Valladolid, Escuela Ingn Ind, Dept CMeIM EGI ICGF IM IPF, Ingn Proc Fabricac, Paseo Cauce 59, E-47011 Valladolid, Spain.
   de Tiedra, Pilar, Univ Valladolid, Escuela Ingn Ind, Dept CMeIM EGI ICGF IPF, Ciencia Mat \& Ingn Met, Paseo Cauce 59, E-47011 Valladolid, Spain.},
DOI = {10.1007/s00170-022-10444-4},
EarlyAccessDate = {NOV 2022},
Keywords = {Explainable boosting machine; Pattern recognition; Quality assessment;
   Resistance spot welding; AISI 304 austenitic stainless steel; Tensile
