   Shen, Zhuoheng; Sun, Yue; Li, Yang; Zhang, Qi; Liu, Yifei; Han, Jiyan; Liu, Zhihong; Guan, Suzhen; Sun, Jian, Key Lab Environm Factors \& Chron Dis Control, Yinchuan 750004, Ningxia, Peoples R China.
