   Benn, Bryan S.; Koth, Laura L., Univ Calif San Francisco, Dept Med, San Francisco, CA USA.
   Lippitt, William L.; Carlson, Nichole E., Colorado Sch Publ Hlth, Dept Biostat \& Informat, Aurora, CO USA.
