   Cozzi-Lepri, Alessandro; Phillips, Andrew, UCL, London, England.
   Brun-Vezinet, Francoise, Hosp Bichat Claude Bernard, Paris, France.
   DeGruttola, Victor, Harvard Univ, Sch Publ Hlth, Boston, MA 02115 USA.
