   Azzam, Taj, Tishreen Mil Hosp, Dept Internal Med, Div Endocrinol \& Diabet, Damascus, Syria.
   Hanafi, Bayan, Damascus Univ, Dept Radiol, Fac Med, Damascus, Syria.
   Sallam, Sondos, Damascus Hosp, Dept Internal Med, Div Pulmonol, Damascus, Syria.
   Khamis, Majd Abu, Al Rasheed Int Private Univ Sci \& Technol, Fac Pharm, Damascus, Syria.
