   Nolte, Svea; Shehab, Naser B. N.; Berger, Stefan P.; van Londen, Marco; Bakker, Stephan J. L., Univ Groningen, Univ Med Ctr Groningen, Dept Internal Med, Div Nephrol, Groningen, Netherlands.
   Nolte, Ilja M., Univ Groningen, Univ Med Ctr Groningen, Dept Epidemiol, Groningen, Netherlands.
   de Greef, Bianca T. A.; Faber, Catharina G., Maastricht Univ, Mental Hlth \& Neurosci HHeNS Res Inst, Med Ctr, Dept Neurol, Maastricht, Netherlands.
