   Duncan, Michael J.; Heering, Theresa; Tallis, Jason; Guimaraes-Ferreira, Lucas; Martins, Ricardo; Crotti, Matteo, Coventry Univ, Ctr Phys Act Sport \& Exercise Sci, Coventry, England.
